<div id="imageContent845ac60045f7482383fad5107663afc1">
</div>


		
Disabled parking between gates 2 and 3 on Little Horton Lane, and at the back enterance to the Horton wing at Gate 4.

Ground floor access to Outpatient Department. 

Lift Access to floors.

Wheelchair ramps.
