<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent37617df6ee104dd282298b4187ea1899">
</div>
<p>There are several Pay and Display car parks at St Lukes they are located opposite the hospital next to Gate 2 on Little Horton Lane. The short stay car park in front of the Horton Wing, accessed from Gate 3 on Little Horton Lane. Short stay and disabled car park is at Gate 4 (Holme Top Lane).</p>
